Mother of the senator representing Adamawa Central, Aishatu Dahiru Ahmed (Binani), Hajiya Aishatu Utiya Dahiru has passed on. A family statement released said the deceased died Thursday evening and will be buried on Friday according to Islamic rites. Read the full statement below: Inna Lillaahi wa Inna Ilaihi Rajiuun . We announce the Sudden death of Hajiya Aishatu Utiya Dahiru this evening Thursday 10th December . Janaizza will in Sha Allah hold tomorrow after Jummaâ€™at prayer at An Nur Mosque. She is survived by her husband several relations and children including Distingished Senator. Aishatu Dahiru Ahmed ( Binani ). Professor Ahmed Modibbo for the family